data.description: Don't miss out of this adorable cape cod style home with natural wood work throughout. Located near McKinley Park with a large back yard perfect for entertaining. Enjoy your evenings on the large deck in the warm months or cozy up by the fireplace in winter. This home features many updates, such new hot water heater, new roof and gutters in 2021, and new HVAC unit installed in 2019. This is a great home that is waiting for its new owners.
